OL,6,FA truck driver has been jailed after
OL,7,Fbeing caught drink driving on the M5
OL,8,Fin Somerset.
OL,10,FPolice were alerted to an HGV swerving
OL,11,Fbetween the hard shoulder and lane one
OL,12,Fby a member of the public on the
OL,13,Fafternoon of Monday 5 February.
OL,15,FSpecial Constables Danny Hopkins and
OL,16,FKalvin Mackenzie managed to locate the
OL,17,Fvehicle and witnessed the driver
OL,18,Fswerve and break hard to avoid a car
OL,19,Fjoining at junction 22 of the motorway.
