OL,6,FThe pair pulled the lorry over and
OL,7,Ffound the man behind the wheel, Ihar
OL,8,FShynkevich, was more than three times
OL,9,Fover the limit, following a roadside
OL,10,Fbreath test.
OL,12,FThe 35-year-old was arrested at
OL,13,FSedgemoor service station and he was
OL,14,Fsubsequently charged with driving a
OL,15,Fmotor vehicle while over the alcohol
OL,16,Flimit.
