OL,6,FHe appeared at Taunton Magistrates
OL,7,FCourt the next day and was sentenced
OL,8,Fto 19 weeks imprisonment, in addition
OL,9,Fto being disqualified from driving for
OL,10,F1,163 days.
OL,12,FThe lorry that Shynkevich, of no fixed
OL,13,Faddress, was driving was found to have
OL,14,Fbeen carrying cargo weighing more than
OL,15,F21 tonnes.
