OL,6,FRoads Policing Acting Inspector
OL,7,FStephen Whatley said: "Considering the
OL,8,Fsize of Shynkevich's vehicle, the
OL,9,Fweight of the load he was carrying and
OL,10,Fthe manner of his driving on a busy
OL,11,Fstretch of carriageway, there could
OL,12,Feasily have been a major collision on
OL,13,Fthe M5 that afternoon.
OL,15,F"Fortunately, this was avoided and a
OL,16,Fdangerous driver has now been taken
OL,17,Foff the roads thanks to a report from
OL,18,Fa member of the public.
