OL,6,F"Given the seriousness of the
OL,7,Fcircumstances, a custodial sentence is
OL,8,Fappropriate and welcomed."
OL,10,F255 people have been arrested for
OL,11,Fdrink driving, while 153 have been
OL,12,Farrested for drug driving by Avon and
OL,13,FSomerset Police since the new year. By
OL,14,Fcomparison, 324 drivers were arrested
OL,15,Fin December during the force's annual
OL,16,Fwinter operation targeting drink and
OL,17,Fdrug drivers.
